headline.main: To the Cabby Who Picked Me Up Near MoMA: Sorry
headline.print_headline: To the Cabby Who Picked Me Up Near MoMA: Sorry

lead_paragraph: Bolivian President Evo Morales has left Cuba after being hospitalized for medical problems and is in Venezuela's capital to participate in a meeting of the ALBA bloc.
